Title: Bloodsport
Plot: After a beloved college football coach is found dead and his house drenched and spattered with his blood, the CSI team hunts for the killer who didn't find Coach Jimmy lovable at all.
ParentalRatingReason: R16 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Jorja Fox, John Carroll Lynch, Josh Henderson, Christopher Rich, Mike Erwin, Sheeri Rappaport
